却似毫无感觉，仍然低着头在吃饭。 心眉大师也已耸然失色，嗄声道：快，快以丹田之气收住心脉。 那些少林僧人居然还不知道是怎么回事，赔笑道：师叔是在吩咐我们？ 心眉大师急着道：自然是吩咐你们，你们中了毒难道连一点都感觉不出？ 少林僧人道：中了毒？谁中了毒？──－ 四人对望一眼，同时叫了起来，你的脸怎的──－ 一句话未说完，四个人已同时倒了下去，等心眉大师再看他们，四张脸都已变了形状，眼鼻五官都已抽搐到一起。 传统武侠小说经常会有“菜里有毒”“酒里有毒”之类的桥段，诚心发问，为啥网文很少有这类桥段嘞？"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ii6rW2tfP5tAaEAMaCDY1OTU4NzgzIMmhxoYGMAk4dUAtcgk0NjY1NTY2NzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1624412543.6998584","card_id":"Q_379247015","target":{"id":379247015,"title":"书荒了，可以推荐一下你最近反复看的小说吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/379247015","type":"question","created":1584109251,"answer_count":233,"follower_count":513,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[73,44871,93542],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"什么类型的都可以"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ii6rW2tfP5tAaEAMaCDQ2NTU1NzY0IMOtrvMFMAM4gQRALnIJMzc5MjQ3MDE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-219196226116a9192f15aed756f9aedc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"47_1624412543.7001822","card_id":"Q_387563344","target":{"id":387563344,"title":"有没有好看的非人物微信头像?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/387563344","type":"question","created":1586792481,"answer_count":89,"follower_count":1287,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1820,10865,68197],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"想找一些头像。不追星，不用明星照片做头像，也不喜欢用真人的头像，感觉拿了不认识的人的照片做头像很尴尬，所以网上好多好看女生照片的头像我都不想用，当然也不会用自己的照片做头像，想问问大家有没有非人物的头像，静物，风景，油画，动画之类的都可以，谢谢大家。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ii6rW2tfP5tAaEAMaCDQ4NDAyNzY2IKGQ0vQFMAE4hwpAL3IJMzg3NTYzMzQ0eACqAQliaWx